TypeSignature.Value: .class public auto ansi sealed JSToken extends System.Enum

summary.span: 指定组成 JScript 语言的单个代码单元或标记。

span.span: Specifies the individual units of code, or *tokens*, that make up the JScript language.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 扫描程序和分析器使用此枚举的成员来读取源代码。The members of this enumeration are used by the scanner and the parser to read source code. 此枚举的成员也由运算符类用于标识要执行的操作。The members of this enumeration are also used by operator classes to identify the operation to perform. 有关详细信息，请参阅[为.NET Framework 创建语言编译器](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=110392)。For more information, see [Create a Language Compiler for the .NET Framework](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=110392).
